<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RM Scheduler</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#F5F4EF;--surface:#ECEBE6;--border:#545454;--accent:#BBCBCD;--accent2:#8FA8AB;--text:#2a2a2a;--muted:#767676;--danger:#c0392b;--success:#27ae60;--white:#fff;--shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh}
#loginScreen{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:1000}
.login-box{background:#fff;padding:48px 40px;width:320px;border-radius:4px}
.login-box h1{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
.login-box p{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:28px}
.login-box input{width:100%;padding:12px 14px;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:3px;font-size:15px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:12px;outline:none}
.login-box input:focus{border-color:var(--border)}
.login-box button{width:100%;padding:13px;background:var(--border);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:3px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif}
.login-err{font-size:12px;color:var(--danger);margin-top:8px;display:none}
header{background:var(--border);color:#fff;padding:0 32px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
header h1{font-size:16px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:1px}
header nav{display:flex;gap:4px}
header nav button{padding:7px 16px;border:none;border-radius:3px;background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;transition:all .15s}
header nav button.active,header nav button:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);color:#fff}
.page{display:none;padding:32px;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto}
.page.active{display:block}
.card{background:#fff;border-radius:6px;padding:28px;margin-bottom:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.card-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--surface)}
.form-row{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px}
.col2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.col3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}
.form-group label{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px}
.form-group input,.form-group select,.form-group textarea{width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:3px;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;background:#fff;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.form-group input:focus,.form-group select:focus,.form-group textarea:focus{border-color:var(--accent2)}
.form-group textarea{min-height:100px;resize:vertical}
.check-group{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.check-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 12px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:20px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:all .15s;user-select:none}
.check-item input{display:none}
.check-item.checked{background:var(--border);border-color:var(--border);color:#fff}
.time-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(72px,1fr));gap:6px;margin-top:8px}
.time-slot{padding:7px 4px;text-align:center;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;transition:all .15s;user-select:none}
.time-slot.selected{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent2);color:var(--border);font-weight:500}
.day-time-row{padding:10px 14px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:8px;background:#fafafa}
.day-time-row .dlabel{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--border);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}
.day-time-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px}
.time-chip{padding:5px 10px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;transition:all .15s;user-select:none;background:#fff}
.time-chip.on{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent2);color:var(--border);font-weight:600}
.btn{padding:10px 22px;border:none;border-radius:3px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;transition:all .15s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.btn-primary{background:var(--border);color:#fff}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#3a3a3a}
.btn-accent{background:var(--accent);color:var(--border)}
.btn-accent:hover{background:var(--accent2);color:#fff}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;border:1.5px solid var(--border);color:var(--border)}
.btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--border);color:#fff}
.btn-sm{padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px}
.btn-copy{padding:6px 14px;background:var(--accent);color:var(--border);border:none;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;transition:all .2s}
.btn-copy.copied{background:var(--success);color:#fff}
.ins-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:16px}
.ins-card{border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:5px;padding:18px;transition:all .15s;position:relative}
.ins-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent2)}
.ins-card .iname{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
.ins-card .isub{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.ins-card .badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;margin:2px}
.edit-btn{position:absolute;top:12px;right:12px;padding:4px 10px;background:transparent;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--muted)}
.edit-btn:hover{border-color:var(--border);color:var(--border)}
.slot-result{border:1.5px solid var(--accent2);border-radius:5px;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:8px;background:#f0f5f5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.slot-result:hover{background:var(--accent)}
.slot-result.chosen{background:var(--border);color:#fff;border-color:var(--border)}
.slot-result .si{font-size:15px;font-weight:500}
.slot-result .sm{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}
.slot-result.chosen .sm{color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.msg-block{border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:5px;margin-bottom:14px;overflow:hidden}
.msg-header{background:var(--surface);padding:10px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0}
.msg-header span{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px}
.msg-tag{font-size:11px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:500}
.msg-tag.ins{background:#ffeaa0;color:#856400}
.msg-tag.stu{background:#a8e6c4;color:#1a6638}
.msg-body{padding:16px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;background:#fff}
.msg-actions{padding:10px 16px;background:#fafafa;border-top:1px solid #e0e0e0;display:flex;justify-content:flex-end}
.tab-bar{display:flex;margin-bottom:24px;border-bottom:2px solid #e0e0e0}
.tab{padding:10px 22px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-2px;transition:all .15s}
.tab.active{color:var(--border);border-bottom-color:var(--border)}
.steps{display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:28px}
.step{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
.step .num{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:#e0e0e0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:700}
.step.active .num{background:var(--border);color:#fff}
.step.done .num{background:var(--success);color:#fff}
.step-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:#e0e0e0;margin:0 8px}
.modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:500}
.modal-overlay.open{display:flex}
.modal{background:#fff;border-radius:8px;padding:32px;width:90%;max-width:640px;max-height:88vh;overflow-y:auto}
.modal h2{font-size:18px;margin-bottom:20px}
.modal-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:24px}
.gcal-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px;background:#fce4ec;color:#c62828}
.gcal-bar .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--danger)}
.notice{background:#fff8e1;border-left:3px solid #f9a825;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin-bottom:16px}
.sec-title{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
.sec-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:24px}
.empty{text-align:center;padding:48px;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px}
.mt16{margin-top:16px}
.type-toggle{display:flex;gap:0;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:4px}
.type-toggle button{flex:1;padding:9px 0;border:none;background:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;color:var(--muted);transition:all .15s}
.type-toggle button.active{background:var(--border);color:#fff}
.checklist-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:8px;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;transition:all .15s;user-select:none}
.checklist-item:hover{border-color:var(--accent2)}
.checklist-item.done{background:#f0f8f0;border-color:var(--success);color:var(--muted);text-decoration:line-through}
.checklist-item .chk{width:20px;height:20px;border:2px solid #ccc;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .15s}
.checklist-item.done .chk{background:var(--success);border-color:var(--success);color:#fff}
.hotkey-box{background:#f8f8f8;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:4px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center}
.hotkey-box .hk{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.hotkey-box .key{background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ccc;border-radius:3px;padding:3px 10px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;box-shadow:0 2px 0 #ccc}
.time-direct-input{padding:5px 8px;border:1.5px dashed #ccc;border-radius:3px;font-size:12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;width:72px;outline:none;color:var(--border)}
.time-direct-input:focus{border-color:var(--accent2)}
.flex-time-wrap{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center}
.flex-time-wrap select{flex:1}
.flex-time-wrap input{width:90px;padding:9px 10px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:3px;font-size:13px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;outline:none}
.flex-time-wrap input:focus{border-color:var(--accent2)}
.flex-time-wrap .sep{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap}
.ai-upload-area{border:2px dashed #ccc;border-radius:6px;padding:24px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;background:#fafafa}
.ai-upload-area:hover,.ai-upload-area.drag{border-color:var(--accent2);background:#f0f5f5}
.ai-upload-area input{display:none}
.ai-upload-area.paste-ready{border-color:var(--accent2);background:#f0f5f5}
.ai-preview-item{position:relative;display:inline-block}
.ai-preview-item img{width:90px;height:68px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;display:block}
.ai-preview-item .del-btn{position:absolute;top:-6px;right:-6px;width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--danger);color:#fff;border:none;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;line-height:1;padding:0}
.paste-hint{font-size:12px;color:var(--accent2);margin-top:8px;text-align:center}
.home-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:5px 14px;background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;margin-bottom:16px;transition:all .15s}
.home-btn:hover{border-color:var(--border);color:var(--border)}
.step-nav{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:20px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.step-nav .snav{padding:5px 14px;background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}
.step-nav .snav:hover{border-color:var(--border);color:var(--border)}
.time-chip{-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none}
.time-chip.selecting{background:var(--accent2);border-color:var(--accent2);color:#fff}
.manual-input-box{border:2px dashed #e0e0e0;border-radius:6px;padding:16px;margin-top:12px;background:#fafafa}
.manual-input-box.visible{display:block}
.no-sched-msg{background:#fff8e1;border-left:3px solid #f9a825;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;margin:8px 0}
.mode-bar{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.mode-btn{flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:12px 8px;border:2px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:6px;background:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;color:var(--muted);transition:all .15s;text-align:center}
.mode-btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent2);color:var(--border)}
.mode-btn.active{border-color:var(--border);background:var(--border);color:#fff}
.mode-section{display:none}
.mode-section.visible{display:block}
.ai-result-slot{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 12px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:6px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:all .15s}
.ai-result-slot:hover{border-color:var(--accent2);background:#f0f5f5}
.ai-result-slot.picked{background:var(--border);color:#fff;border-color:var(--border)}
.range-select{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px}
.range-btn{padding:5px 14px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;background:#fff;font-family:inherit;transition:all .15s}
.range-btn.active{background:var(--border);color:#fff;border-color:var(--border)}
body.drag-selecting{cursor:grabbing}
body.drag-selecting .time-chip{transition:none}

.slot-group{border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:6px;margin:10px 0 12px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden}
.slot-group[open]{box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}
.slot-group summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;padding:12px 14px;background:#fafafa;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--border);user-select:none}
.slot-group summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
.slot-group summary .group-title{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.slot-group summary .count{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:12px;padding:2px 8px}
.slot-group summary .chev{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);transition:transform .15s}
.slot-group[open] summary .chev{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.slot-group-body{padding:8px 10px 10px}
.slot-group-body .slot-result:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.slot-category-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);padding:0 2px 8px;line-height:1.5}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="loginScreen">
  <div class="login-box">
    <h1>RM Scheduler</h1>
    <p>라이언멤버스 행정팀 전용</p>
    <input type="password" id="pwInput" placeholder="비밀번호 입력" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')doLogin()">
    <button onclick="doLogin()">로그인</button>
    <div class="login-err" id="loginErr">비밀번호가 올바르지 않습니다.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<header>
  <h1>RM SCHEDULER</h1>
  <nav>
    <button class="active" onclick="showPage('scheduling',this)">📅 스케쥴링</button>
    <button onclick="showPage('instructors',this)">👤 강사 설정</button>
    <button onclick="showPage('settings',this)">⚙️ 설정</button>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- SCHEDULING -->
<div id="page-scheduling" class="page active">
  <div class="sec-title">신규 학생 스케쥴링</div>
  <div class="sec-sub">학생 정보 입력 → 최적 일정 자동 추천 → 메세지 생성</div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step active" id="si1"><div class="num">1</div><span>학생 정보</span></div>
    <div class="step-line"></div>
    <div class="step" id="si2"><div class="num">2</div><span>일정 추천</span></div>
    <div class="step-line"></div>
    <div class="step" id="si3"><div class="num">3</div><span>메세지 생성</span></div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 1 -->
  <div id="step1">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">학생 기본 정보</div>
      <div class="form-row col2">
        <div class="form-group"><label>학생 이름 *</label><input type="text" id="s-name" placeholder="예: 김민지"></div>
        <div class="form-group"><label>전화번호 *</label><input type="text" id="s-phone" placeholder="예: 010-1234-5678"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row col2">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>레벨</label>
          <select id="s-level"><option value="">선택</option><option>Lv.1</option><option>Lv.2</option><option>Lv.3</option></select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>담당 강사 지정 (복수 가능 · 미선택 시 전체 추천)</label>
          <div class="check-group" id="s-instructor-direct" style="margin-top:4px"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>수업 과목 * (복수 선택 가능)</label>
        <div class="check-group" id="s-subjects"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">수업 조건</div>
      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:20px">
        <label>수업 유형</label>
        <div class="type-toggle">
          <button id="type-fixed" class="active" onclick="setLessonType('fixed')">고정식</button>
          <button id="type-flex" onclick="setLessonType('flex')">비고정식</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="fixed-fields">
      <div class="form-row col2" style="margin-bottom:20px">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>주당 수업 횟수</label>
          <select id="s-freq" onchange="onFreqChange()">
            <option value="1">주 1회</option><option value="2" selected>주 2회</option>
            <option value="3">주 3회</option><option value="5">주 5회</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>1회 수업 시간</label>
          <div class="flex-time-wrap">
            <select id="s-duration">
              <option value="1" selected>1시간</option>
              <option value="1.5">1시간 30분</option>
              <option value="2">2시간</option>
            </select>
            <span class="sep">또는 직접</span>
            <input type="text" id="s-duration-direct" placeholder="예: 1.5" style="width:70px;padding:9px 10px;border:1.5px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:3px;font-size:13px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;outline:none">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:16px">
        <label>희망 요일 선택 (주당 횟수만큼)</label>
        <div class="check-group" id="s-days"></div>
      </div>
      <div id="dayTimePicker" style="display:none">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>요일별 희망 시간</label>
          <div id="dayTimeRows"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

      </div><!-- /fixed-fields -->
      <!-- 비고정식: 강사 지정 안내 -->
      <div id="flex-fields" style="display:none">
        <div class="notice" style="margin-top:4px">비고정식은 담당 강사를 위에서 지정해주세요. 다음 단계에서 강사의 빈 시간을 확인해 첫 수업 슬롯을 선택합니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px">
